{"tid":2251263,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陳肇始回應傳遭建制派篤灰求撤換：我冇補充  李梓敬曾批：廢官，淨係識喊","createTime":"2020-10-20T16:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T00:52:49.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac4307c59690b9b774087f05d2702d66cbd96f18","tid":2251263,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T16:15:11.000Z","msg":"護士出身的食衞局局長陳肇始，持有曼徹斯特大學教育碩士、哈佛大學公共衞生碩士及香港大學哲學博士學位，出任局長以來，表現未如理想。去年回應傳媒查詢國產催淚彈成份時，坦承當局對成份的無知，稱當局只是翻查文獻，向公眾提供清洗催淚煙指引。今年陳局長領軍抗疫亦未孚眾望，限聚令進退失據，實施全日禁堂食天怒人怨，翌日即告取消更離地謂「禁堂食先發現好多人仲要返工」 。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，除了政界人士不滿陳肇始表現，不少公立醫生對陳都有微言，認為她冇料到，能力不足，今次抗疫的甩碌表現可見一斑。不過，有政界中心認為由於距離林鄭特首任期結束不足兩年，加上未必有人肯接這個燙手山芋，相信中央不會輕言撤換陳肇始。「佢應該可以平平安安做埋嗰年幾嘅，但係下屆就唔使旨意冧莊。」<br />\n<br />\n建制中人如李梓敬今年7月亦於facebook批陳肇始：「陳肇始係廢官，我話嘅。」斥陳未「嚴懲逃兵醫護」之餘，亦沒有一早要求向歐美來港人士強制隔離，禁堂食朝令夕改，「淨係識得喊」。公民黨郭家麒年初在武肺未於香港爆發前，已拍片呼籲市民要靠自己做好防禦措施，「唔好靠政府」，舉例指台灣澳門等鄰近地區已加強陸路口岸檢疫，對所有從武漢抵達的旅客量度體溫，惟港府當時仍不動如山，斥陳肇始是肺炎的「廢」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201020/CWNQLCDDUZCZXF645E57TF3ZX4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201020%2FCWNQLCDDUZCZXF645E57TF3ZX4%2F&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=bb8bf2aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201020%2FCWNQLCDDUZCZXF645E57TF3ZX4%2F&h=da5cf1ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201020/CWNQLCDDUZCZXF645E57TF3ZX4/</a>"},{"pid":"c1acebd7d80baf0a2f6786c35ea1ecf1929013e6","tid":2251263,"uid":76804,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T16:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image1.thenewslens.com/2019/6/chijx5u3ycishrlzd3528d22vcdsc3.jpg?auto=compress&amp;h=648&amp;q=80&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage1.thenewslens.com%2F2019%2F6%2Fchijx5u3ycishrlzd3528d22vcdsc3.jpg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26h%3D648%26q%3D80%26w%3D1080&h=e4c09c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">廢官 淨係識喊</span>"},{"pid":"5dfafeda7c612ba86eef3ba6dde1ba00ce875abc","tid":2251263,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T16:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af3411117c92c95b39273aa65172917db2650bb","tid":2251263,"uid":94314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T17:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> condom1號 武漢肺炎果期擋完箭就比人棄"},{"pid":"1e3c9a3dd323728199747c8453d4018c97965738","tid":2251263,"uid":121197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T00:44:13.000Z","msg":"30萬人工一個月<br />\n俾人屌係廢官都無所謂啦"},{"pid":"dd46e9927fdb38952154204a2859991bdbf73c78","tid":2251263,"uid":39974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T00:45:01.000Z","msg":"鬥藍"},{"pid":"a31840055313deeef78a161acd0c3b198589748a","tid":2251263,"uid":60868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T00:45:53.000Z","msg":"西門紙莖咪又係廢人一個<br />\n全撚部去死啦"},{"pid":"aa4468b08c743ec2ad4ac08688900bf60d988a14","tid":2251263,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c1acebd7d80baf0a2f6786c35ea1ecf1929013e6","tid":2251263,"uid":76804,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T16:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image1.thenewslens.com/2019/6/chijx5u3ycishrlzd3528d22vcdsc3.jpg?auto=compress&amp;h=648&amp;q=80&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage1.thenewslens.com%2F2019%2F6%2Fchijx5u3ycishrlzd3528d22vcdsc3.jpg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26h%3D648%26q%3D80%26w%3D1080&h=e4c09c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">廢官 淨係識喊</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T00:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/AarXuE9wcvg/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FAarXuE9wcvg%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=33360416&s={SIZE}\" 